From c06668164acd00d1360077ac21854b2848707828 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Devajith V S <devajithvs@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 26 Nov 2020 17:58:10 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 119/163] arm64: dts: qcom: msm8916-asus-z010d: add display
 panel (v2)

