From 419beff64dc768026ada4e562e135858d893c80e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Lin, Meng-Bo" <linmengbo0689@protonmail.com>
Date: Mon, 28 Nov 2022 13:15:12 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 124/163] arm64: dts: qcom: msm8916-acer-a1-724: Add display
 panel

